{"tid":1654493,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[你講我整]一人一首致香港現況廣東歌","createTime":"2019-10-14T15:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T22:45:03.000Z","uid":19793,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"f45f2e55ce5e5f1af929a569fe4a0562e2d36cfc","tid":1654493,"uid":19793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"利申 手腳慢 唔好見怪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CedzvZb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCedzvZb.jpg&h=c286cb4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vSkrxC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vSkrxC.jpg&h=bedd1e08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pi1dMxH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPi1dMxH.jpg&h=4e1504a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dswJpjs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdswJpjs.jpg&h=be1f9561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ue3zvZy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fue3zvZy.jpg&h=f8a05ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7d7QZF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7d7QZF.jpg&h=29095274&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwKbyc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwKbyc5.jpg&h=bf8ab319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fB9u4jR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfB9u4jR.jpg&h=45d37b40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91a53466776b7ddc10f4059547def3ca9724e1ac","tid":1654493,"uid":143730,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T18:11:52.000Z","msg":"高質 支持<br />\n周國賢 雪國<br />\n''來讚頌人民革命 相信他你必有永久保證''"},{"pid":"b55b01e9d5aed9b03fd64170c0a0288446