5743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"第一個諗到，竟然係呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林峯，馴獸師之王，Gphone都識<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xiG511s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxiG511s.png&h=f911d3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家睇返真係好應境，每次發夢都對住啲popo，香港人真係要進化成馴獸師之王<br />\n一代神曲，露營必須洒，未來係煲底必須洒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:34:57.000Z","msg":"日文原版仲要係 biggest dreamer<br />\n真&middot;發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c7d854206e8351798650ea488554c3791a5cce","tid":1654493,"uid":302000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:44:52.000Z","msg":"戰爭-陳冠希<br />\n<br />\nTo 真。香港人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">打 我而家就去打仗 打屬於我自己嘅一場仗<br />\n假若現實世界根本就係一個戰場<br />\n咁一切現象係咪一對殘酷假象<br />\n假如現實要我去打一場假仗<br />\n打住乜野旗號 打一場點樣嘅仗<br />\n打得唔好我嘅生命就此劃上句號<br />\n問得唔好 我應該問生命一個乜野問號<br />\n問我 悲哭聲可以有幾多幾多<br />\n問我童謠用乜野號角可以吹乜野悲歌<br />\n歌舞昇平嘅世界 幾可聽到凱旋歌曲<br />\n曲終人散嘅時候 只有剩低幾個幾個<br />\n我問我 我嘅戰友係咪就係我一個<br />\n我為我 嘅生命戰鬥要我保衛我<br />\n我話我 進一步退一步 我都難過</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTo 偽中立果班<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">你同我同佢邊個 可以選擇做旁觀者<br />\n無人會鍾意見到 遍地死者<br />\n無人會鍾意做 戰地記者<br />\n唔想知道乜野叫做戰爭罪行<br />\n剩係知道呢度法律唔保障所有嘅人</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTo PoPo和七婆<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">成日要名要利 沖沖沖從未識死<br />\n再不分戰場屋企 愛人知己 我想勝利<br />\n行或企如戰地 很想死而未敢死 是我想得太盡要爭氣</span></span>"},{"pid":"089eb1bb399f565f8694881795e0d2c98b774655","tid":1654493,"uid":246781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:46:27.000Z","msg":"Beyond - 抗戰二十年<br />\n而家先想放棄？"},{"pid":"be5693869ba159186c197c6c9729bbb60b2ddc9b","tid":1654493,"uid":19793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33142d7f53f25cbc43980f5be229701385271cf2","tid":1654493,"uid":183576,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"謝安琪-獨家村<br />\n我亦很怕一心軟 會將就得更辛酸<br />\n換到飽暖失去自己一世不甘願"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UsVbmxU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUsVbmxU.jpg&h=5872c2d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc1a5015600f43e2492dec9e185d7fab5ef654f7","tid":1654493,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:50:06.000Z","msg":"若被傷害夠，就用一對手，痛快的割開昨日詛咒。 入夜等白晝，剩下傷痕開始結焦，那胸膛。 城內快要變作困獸鬥，人人尋仇赤腳走。"},{"pid":"273561b6a444a38b731aa3d9cd0998b6496fd672","tid":1654493,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:51:11.000Z","msg":"願你知每日每夜為何戰鬥"},{"pid":"c2615650c9580324b586440a0c1527f5fd94a067","tid":1654493,"uid":19793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aa720f92cb1235e99081a351cc77f2b0931738c","tid":1654493,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"王菲-白痴<br />\n<br />\n哪怕沒有辦法一定有說法 就算沒有鴿子一定有烏鴉<br />\n固執無罪 夢想有價 讓他們驚訝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFBh1yv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFBh1yv.jpg&h=1321b6a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e1e389ca2d328867f836b3f94f40a89906e333a","tid":1654493,"uid":247311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:52:20.000Z","msg":"《江山(節錄)》 馬德鐘<br />\n<br />\n未歸路　終需要還<br />\n浪很大　用全力再挽<br />\n汗水來　烽火照出這肝膽<br />\n在經歷　多少困難<br />\n在感受　別離共慨嘆<br />\n看長空　千種恩怨　引刀斬<br />\n<br />\n踏世上　高峰總要攀　碧血染青衫<br />\n笑中看變幻　算破綻　一子決江山<br />\n成敗瞬間　隻手風雨翻<br />\n打拼過千關　再不會折返<br />\n踏世上　高峰總要攀　碧血染青衫<br />\n揭開了戰幔　算破綻　一子決江山<br />\n成敗瞬間　隻手風雨翻<br />\n虧欠我江山　你總要奉還"},{"pid":"34d0476e801dd1e1e24805dbfc1c930920de634c","tid":1654493,"uid":19793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e7003eb9665cfaa524d9bfb0fcdbd87f06b29a5","tid":1654493,"uid":183576,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:28:48.000Z","msg":"盧巧音-好心分手<br />\n<br />\n回頭望 伴你走 從來未曾幸福過<br />\n赴過湯 蹈過火 沿途為何沒愛河<br />\n下半生 陪住你 懷疑快樂也不多<br />\n沒有心 別再拖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想將呢段詞送比中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6WRmyO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6WRmyO.jpg&h=e4f4fce9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfea0bd25fed7215294521f8c0ee5a14f5ea9e5c","tid":1654493,"uid":195088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:53:27.000Z","msg":"Per se<br />\n天空塌下前<br />\n<br />\n散聚故事 說若說不完（ 天空望見）<br />\n故事嗎 讓我為你補完<br />\n<br />\n一轉念 前路沒新 發現<br />\n離別未說 為何未說<br />\n更亂<br />\n<br />\n就到終點 你縱然看不見 （天空 塌下前 洶湧 退浪前）<br />\n再難過的 任重道仍漫長 路雖漸遠 （路若漫長 靠近我 不忙亂）<br />\n無從兌現 奮勇無悔不變 （青春 刺痛時 光陰 散落時）<br />\n那無畏的 豔色青春 人生的 盛宴 （路就在前 請捉緊一點）<br />\n前進的 用心開闢 未舖的路 在前（都可改變）"},{"pid":"8d18f416c3f19d461c6b94321971e58a44945cc6","tid":1654493,"uid":19793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a089442bf10817302260708446f40f874aafe4e5","tid":1654493,"uid":81477,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"發過要發的夢 但熱烈漸覺冰凍<br />\n跌過痛過便會懂<br />\n誰在作弄 沉默背後也想發狂<br />\n很想找一剎來放縱 斗膽一次如反恐<br />\n<br />\n也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝<br />\n衝出困局 形象似義勇軍般英勇<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通<br />\n<br />\n如戴著面具去掩飾倦容<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 懷着理想哪怕痛(忘卻世間的縳束)<br />\n<br />\n誰明白像和你也許重逢<br />\n遺憾太多卻不能倒流的鐘<br />\n如琴聲的哀號 連結他都哭訴<br />\n誰明白我初衷 煩躁也是個夢 但我真的痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NV4ocFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNV4ocFS.jpg&h=ee01a05b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a3a80884c3de7856d4c6e0a72a8875c35cc1a53","tid":1654493,"uid":19793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"81bca44ab33d856cf1e96ad722847fe17afe7d4a","tid":1654493,"uid":195905,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:32:16.000Z","msg":"今日 陳奕迅<br />\n抬頭吧 黑暗過會是晨曦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:54:44.000Z","msg":"黎明前嘅黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPaOoNN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPaOoNN.jpg&h=b48accfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ff216fd65da00ac7dfa264c2d3a8b8b85e87bf3","tid":1654493,"uid":247311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:54:53.000Z","msg":"《追夢者》古巨基<br />\n我沒有放不低的散聚<br />\n捍衛我要堅守的壯舉<br />\n我沒有過不到的畏懼<br />\n無視那誣蔑我的判罪<br />\n<br />\n紛擾的世界總會有唏噓<br />\n誰亦有維護理想的血淚<br />\n消失的證據未曾磨滅著過去<br />\n和我面對雨打風吹<br />\n<br />\n仍執著一個信念無論結果撐下去<br />\n血脈未靜似水怎會絕望疲累<br />\n一些過去一些面具放下埋進土裏<br />\n自尊教我面對刧難亦是無懼<br />\n<br />\n仍想像總會有日能讓你知我是對<br />\n趁著陣陣雨水准我靜靜流淚<br />\n得失進退千秋萬代那管天崩山粉碎<br />\n曾歷劫未怕艱辛日後再聚<br />\n<br />\n紛擾的世界總會有唏噓<br />\n誰亦有維護理想的血淚<br />\n消失的證據未曾磨滅著過去<br />\n和我面對雨打風吹<br />\n<br />\n仍執著一個信念無論結果撐下去<br />\n血脈未靜似水怎會絕望疲累<br />\n一些過去一些面具放下埋進土裏<br />\n自尊教我面對刧難亦是無懼<br />\n<br />\n仍想像總會有日能讓你知我是對<br />\n趁著陣陣雨水准我靜靜流淚<br />\n得失進退千秋萬代那管天崩山粉碎<br />\n曾歷劫未怕艱辛日後再聚<br />\n回望最壞那一天伴著有誰<br />\n<br />\n真係發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5489a5190510100d64394c69efc949e62137bd66","tid":1654493,"uid":28470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:55:29.000Z","msg":"陳柏宇 讓子彈飛<br />\n<br />\n開火 為鎮守一個最微細盼望<br />\n無懼遠射炮像煙花放<br />\n為了家一個 這樣脆弱都抵抗<br />\n傷口 倦了的軀幹滲著了血汗<br />\n無論吃敗仗會極之沮喪<br />\n就算多沮喪 拼命拼命的反抗"},{"pid":"bb23244db5f69846f4ce3617641c713068f8a5dd","tid":1654493,"uid":332552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"家明 謝安琪 <br />\n坦克也震開"},{"pid":"b8716969bfaa6d02af1d1095398686ce0036d010","tid":1654493,"uid":10040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:02:21.000Z","msg":"誰知黑與黑 反襯起了紅黃綠白<br />\n何只一片黑 十顏十色的畫冊<br />\n何解竟怕黑 真相總會如期大白<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩 親愛的黑色"},{"pid":"2338fec8e338f88e45a0bdd0ca6f2d396589e675","tid":1654493,"uid":304603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91bfb2049607c65d2602146dd6f94aa6d7f9b03d","tid":1654493,"uid":203332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a2ea85a59fc92db8484dfd18b39c13db81a6f813","tid":1654493,"uid":140924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d94774e3bd8cf26ce886e9322ae074c2ce7eb6af","tid":1654493,"uid":23685,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"謝安琪 家明<br />\n<br />\n最後即使走進浮砂 沉沒中 也會發出光亮嗎 <br />\n臨近破滅一下 要是信任童話 還是有望看到天際白馬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:40:46.000Z","msg":"<strong>時代遍地磚瓦 <br />\n卻欠這種優雅 <br />\n教人夢想不要去談代價</strong><br />\n<br />\n至愛呢一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起健仔 <br />\n諗起許義士 <br />\n諗起梁凌杰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:27:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"呢句真係好中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d924844dbfa245ea545b1d81609abfbbd39c33","tid":1654493,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcbf55bebcbafe4cb69edb93bf588f1b7e3be047","tid":1654493,"uid":3705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8746fe0c0bf4352d5d71ef0e5fe8f1934ce6d106","tid":1654493,"uid":192730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d92b766a50eeb43c14131d933be44fcf84c1c94d","tid":1654493,"uid":192730,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"Kolor 天地會<br />\n老年若記起 少年時曾踏禁地<br />\n揭露各權貴的禁忌<br />\n成長於這世紀<br />\n隨波中一再斷臂<br />\n禁欲禁言禁天禁地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:50:30.000Z","msg":"仲有句<br />\n「城市快將要死，如果這都算正常，你我結這壞帳」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:29:35.000Z","msg":"我最鍾意果段係<br />\n<br />\n「未麻目的 終於會脫離 制度壓迫一朝過期<br />\n    復明現光 青天破八旗 欲蓋是獸皮 人性是契機」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:06:40.000Z","msg":"城市永不會死<br />\n世界有天合唱"},{"pid":"4f47c37f042e2f7dc3497a854a98e230774d56fc","tid":1654493,"uid":19793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4cf7c7909310fb7a65d717d1df528d05a6e76cb0","tid":1654493,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"關楚耀<br />\n我們這一代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小克好多首都係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RsChhji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRsChhji.jpg&h=fdd64df1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c60b87c8b38bd8e7930e3c7048522015dd414354","tid":1654493,"uid":314509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:33:57.000Z","msg":"KOLOR - 生於憂患<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YO8X60SQw50\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYO8X60SQw50&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm952AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=cbf71844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YO8X60SQw50</a><br />\n<br />\n<code>[呢段好具體描述前線嘅經歷]</code><br />\n行完窮途 明白我本性<br />\n見過獸性 正好擦亮着眼睛<br />\n焦慮突襲 磨利我反應<br />\n見識給我見證 寄生憂患習慣受驚<br />\n<br />\n<code>[致前線手足嘅父母]</code><br />\n沒有傷損 怎發育健全<br />\n從沒傷風 怎懂得取暖<br />\n<br />\n<code>[致覺得多事不如少一事嘅人]</code><br />\n麻痹 是半死的開端<br />\n只知道吃喝穿<br />\n<br />\n<code>其實自己鍾意以下幾句多啲\n但諗唔到指明畀咩對象好</code><br />\n/心苦過那怕酸/<br />\n/若怕辛酸 生我在樂園/<br />\n/去過葬禮 如像已死過 滿肚憤慨 我不怕餓/<br />\n<br />\n<code>利申：打手</code><br />\n<br />\n<code>再申：下年八月 九展見！</code>"},{"pid":"1de9a00434eea8b9a19ec33d2a00a1941854e102","tid":1654493,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:45:52.000Z","msg":"KOLOR - i<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WzjNIGoqmU8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWzjNIGoqmU8&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm952AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=c14eb8b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WzjNIGoqmU8</a><br />\n<br />\n<code>致覺得自己食鹽多過人地食米嘅人</code><br />\n誰人都會 在世間過數十年<br />\n精確點 人成長了 尚有一萬五千天<br />\n猿人若不長進 那火箭不會上青天<br />\n徒勞面壁興建 你需遠瞻<br />\n<br />\n<code>致所有無名手足</code><br />\n種子種下一朝開遍地 人想像要越過世紀<br />\n浮名鎖不到你 靈光於千里 誰稀罕明日墓與碑<br />\n<br />\n<code>致靈動如水嘅香港人</code><br />\n創新 因污點太多 連鎖 同時立亦有破<br />\n模範是綁不到我 能拋開本我 人思覺會突破"},{"pid":"f38fb9b5f88d51d86bd1fe3348386b11f5d00fa9","tid":1654493,"uid":215888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:48:36.000Z","msg":"達明一派&mdash;&mdash;十個救火的少年<br />\n在這夜這猛火像燎原　<br />\n大眾（藍絲）議論到這三位少年<br />\n亂說亂說　愈說只有愈遠"},{"pid":"bf3a4e9e4f213f65a7642e18651ea8271be45e2e","tid":1654493,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d94774e3bd8cf26ce886e9322ae074c2ce7eb6af","tid":1654493,"uid":23685,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"謝安琪 家明<br />\n<br />\n最後即使走進浮砂 沉沒中 也會發出光亮嗎 <br />\n臨近破滅一下 要是信任童話 還是有望看到天際白馬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:52:08.000Z","msg":"梁義士<br />\n黎特個MV次次都喊到baba聲"},{"pid":"9fb821e691c5090eb84d9b6daf5aaa2d66d1e1f1","tid":1654493,"uid":314509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>KOLOR - i</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有呢段<br />\n<br />\n<code>致全球抗共最前線嘅香港人</code><br />\n誰人想過 令世間一朝改變 可變天<br />\n誰人相信 在你心裏那起點<br />\n原來自己肯試 會攀到舉世最優先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">大家記得下年仲要一齊睇show跳到拆屋嗌到失聲\n喺呢日之前 1020尖沙咀見！</code></pre>"},{"pid":"ee6cd4e169f3652492555be66f225b4b016316d4","tid":1654493,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:07:50.000Z","msg":"容祖兒 最後的茱麗葉<br />\n<br />\n就算有軍隊封路 圍牆建起 <br />\n都衝得過都也未怕死"},{"pid":"f806b7af248ecd967e154926c7adae2cbbe071cf","tid":1654493,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:30:24.000Z","msg":"何韻詩系列 (打氣為主)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">艷光四射</span></strong><br />\n<code>呢句應該唔洗解啦</code><br />\n生於亂世 有種責任<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光明會</span></strong><br />\n<code>發個好夢</code><br />\n要是你願意 你共我可以 合作改變歷史<br />\n<code>致互不相識嘅手足</code><br />\n這群人不曾同台偏偏不陌生<br />\n分途來修行 發着貼心聲音<br />\n<code>We're at the point of no return</code><br />\n不尋常的人 不平凡的人 不回頭的人<br />\n我們的計劃 就要變真<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">金剛經</span></strong><br />\n<code>承先賢之志 燃革命之火</code><br />\n我們仍然未得勝 還在革命 頑強爭取太平<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">風見志郎</span></strong><br />\n<code>我反你個反蒙面法</code><br />\n沒名字的臉 夕照的剪照 因山水抗戰<br />\n像奇異生物 被世間指點 怪一點點<br />\n/<br />\n幪面青年 入世雖短淺<br />\n都死守 流失的海岸線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">極夜後</span></strong><br />\n<code>我 地 會 贏 !</code><br />\n那一線光 即將散落寸土尺方<br />\n風中依稀聽到了號角<br />\n這片地 終再看到 那艷陽高飛"},{"pid":"a35a0e22017ad81d0bc82a4b6b07879b58c1d6eb","tid":1654493,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5670f8ce23fed3d38e1bac42d9cd13e08c1fa9","tid":1654493,"uid":192730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a35a0e22017ad81d0bc82a4b6b07879b58c1d6eb","tid":1654493,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:44:35.000Z","msg":"唔知你有無聽過<br />\n瓊枝 - 沉香<br />\n逆流 - 變革<br />\n呢兩首都係寫到應一應<br />\n不過太嘈+小眾唔係到po了"}]}